## This repository is an attempt to solve:

https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/bash-completion/+bug/384017


## Using

* replace your /etc/bash_completion with bash_completion script from this repo.
* run `sudo ./update-bash-completion.sh` to create links for command
  that have completion rules grouped in one file

## Comments

The second step is a hack to overcome current design optimizations and could be
eliminated if this solution was adopted for wide use.
